  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Natarran</span> Incense is a be=
autiful
  but subtle perfume made from the <span class=3DSpellE>Natarril</span> pla=
nt.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Natarril</span> is a small shru=
b with
  tiny blue-green leaves and dazzling multi-color flowers. It is typically
  found clinging to rocky cliff-faces on Desert worlds.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Occurrence: very rare</p>
